      • toArray

        java.lang.Object[] toArray()
        Turns a NBT list into a Java array. 
        
     var tag = mappet.createCompound("{id:[0,2,4]}");

     c.send(tag.get("id").toArray()[1]); // 2
        Returns:
        an array of the list's elements
